My husband has looked at these videos for almost ten years, and I finally decided this was the year to get them for him.  The little booklet that accompanies the discs provides side information that gives a nice backdrop to the legendary times.  Very nicely packaged, and nostalgic in nature.  We look forward to many happy hours of comedy from a bygone, less crude, time.
My husband & I were very disappointed  with the tapes, because they are jusst segments of roasts & a lot of talking by Jonathan Winters about Dean Martin.  Very unhappy.
While I got s3veral roasts, there were too many other things for the money

Thoroughly enjoyed this trip down memory lane. It was hilarious watching stuff that would NEVER make it by our oversensitive, butt-hurt society today, yet it was never vulgar, and everyone was subject to be lampooned. Wish the ENTIRE series was available, but maybe one day.
I just love my power rangers. I've been waiting a while to get my hands on this. I always enjoy watching power rangers. It's like taking a trip back in time
